text: Since the wires on the ring are very thin, there is a high chance that after months of constant use some wire could break. Therefore it would be great if such problems were detected automatically by the software.
	
	For example, if it was detected that green channel of the RGB LED is not working, the software could use a combination of red and blue channels to produce a different color as a fallback.
	
